{"type": "article", "id": 12556, "title": "Apple Watch 充电底座", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-24T08:09:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606145507bSjcNVRMKkhaZq0D.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个 Apple Watch 的充电底座，看上去就像一个小企鹅，也像是一个小胖子，当 Apple Watch 放上去后，表盘上会显示一个小眼睛，到处乱看，还可以 “blingbling” 眨眼睛，看起来非常滑稽可爱，颜色上有白色，黄色和黑丝，且附有小胡子等装饰物，一切的目的，都是让你的桌面变得妙趣横生。这里是<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/vivienmuller/watchme\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140253MPKVaq6p2v49unbm.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140255Gpikv4RfsahDTweC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140257hIKWsH34LFAga6yx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140304yEQudHS7FVxa23hp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140309E1MhbpAfkJO9ld6y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.56764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}